{"article_id":"gXOJL2999HhQt6Y8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Democrat Conor Lamb looks likely to have won an incredibly close special election in Pennsylvania ' s 18th Congressional District ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"beating out Republican candidate Rick Saccone in a deeply conservative district","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that the nonpartisan Cook Political Report rates R+11 .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"As of midnight Tuesday , official outlets deemed the race too close to call .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Though a trickle of absentee election ballots were still to be counted late Tuesday night ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"some election watchers predicted","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Lamb would win , albeit by an extremely close margin .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Around midnight , Lamb had 49.9 percent of the vote ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"compared to Saccone ' s 49.5 percent ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"meaning the two candidates were separated by just 847 votes .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"It 's very possible","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"( even likely )","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"that Saccone","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"( R )","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"won the # PA18 Election Day vote .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"barring an error ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"absentees will have put Lamb","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"( D )","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"over the top .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"- Dave Wasserman","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"( @ Redistrict )","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"March 14 , 2018","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"But","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"before the race was officially called ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"the Democratic Congressional Campaign Committee was already celebrating .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"\" I want to congratulate Conor Lamb and his team of grassroots supporters on an incredible victory , \"","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"said DCCC Chair Rep. Ben Ray Luján","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"( NM )","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"in an email","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"sent out around 11:30 pm .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"In a scorching statement , Luján blasted his Republican opponents","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"for dumping millions into a race","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"that they were predicted to lose .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"\" These results should terrify Republicans , \"","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"\" Despite their home field advantage and the millions of dollars","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"outside groups","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"poured into this race ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Republicans found","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"that their attacks against Conor ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"including their unpopular tax scam ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"were not believable .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"There are more than one hundred districts more favorable for Democrats than this one","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"and we look forward to competing hard in every single one . \"","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"Even with the race too close","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"to call ,","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"the result doesn ' t look good for Republicans ,","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"who have held on to PA-18 with an iron grip since 2003 .","depth":4},{"id":49,"text":"The newly open seat was held by former Rep. Tim Murphy since 2003 ,","depth":4},{"id":50,"text":"who was so secure in his seat","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"that he often failed to attract a Democratic challenger .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"Murphy suddenly resigned in October amid revelations","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"that he had pressured a woman","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"with whom he was having an extramarital affair","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"to have an abortion .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"even after he stepped down ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"national Democrats didn ' t think","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"they could compete in the special election ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"one Democratic Congressional Campaign Committee operative told .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"The district went for Donald Trump by nearly 20 points in the 2016 presidential election .","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"Conventional wisdom suggested","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"that Saccone","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"- a candidate","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"who once declared himself \" Trump","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"before Trump was Trump \" -","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"would do well in a district","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"that turned out in droves for Trump .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"But in recent weeks , Republicans were in full panic mode ,","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"dumping more than $ 9 million into the race .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":141,"left":115,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":93,"right":114,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":74,"right":92,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":73,"right":3,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":0,"right":72,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":89,"right":91,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":76,"right":88,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":4,"right":75,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":75,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":88,"left":78,"right":87,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":77,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":87,"left":82,"right":86,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":82,"left":79,"right":